        <h1>How to Run Facebook Ads: A Beginner&rsquo;s Guide That Actually Works</h1>
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>By <strong>Kevin Freeland</strong></span>
          <span>March 14, 2026</span>
          <span>10 min read</span>
        </div>
      </div>
